data.description: Situated in a private cul-de-sac neighborhood in Regency Park, this well cared-for ranch style townhome enjoys the best of both worlds - peaceful surroundings and easy access to shopping, dining, schools, and parks within a short distance. This home boasts an open floor-plan designed with functionality in mind, including the large main bedroom with ensuite and walk-in closet, expansive living room with plenty of natural lighting, ample cabinet and counter space, breakfast nook, private covered-patio and new luxury vinyl plank flooring. Don't miss your chance to own this low maintenance home- it won't last long!
